<http://vocab.linkeddata.es/datosabiertos/def/urbanismo-infraestructuras/aparcamiento#Parking> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Parking for different types of vehicles, including off-street parking facilities or on-street parking zones for residents, non-residents, or free parking."@en .
<http://vocab.linkeddata.es/datosabiertos/def/urbanismo-infraestructuras/aparcamiento#Parking> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Aparcamiento"@es .
